title: #92Noon! Rosie and Nordo on #FinalFour Radio Row, Day 1 [FULL SHOW]
description:
The FAN's Mark Rosen and Eric Nordquist are live from Final Four Radio Row!

Guests include current Long Beach State head coach and former Gophers men's basketball coach Dan Monson, professional boxer Caleb Truax, and former NBA players Robbie Hummel, Jim Jackson, and Jason Terry!
